subSubSection.paragraph:
Remarks. This species is similar to
Epitrimerus armeniacae
Kuang, Luo & Wang, 2005
, but can be differentiated by prodorsal shield with lines arranged irregularly (prodorsal shield with lines arranged regularly in
E. armeniacae
); prosternal apodeme obvious (prosternal apodeme inconspicuous in
E. armeniacae
); female coverflap with two cross lines at base (coverflap without cross lines in
E. armeniacae
).
